target.message:
Excepthook now doesn't raise errors during interpreter shutdown.
These are usually spurious - excepthook simply raises as normal and lets the
threading module deal with it in the usual way.

Also added python3 support fot excepthook, though labscript will not use this anywhere.
This is because I'm planning on realeasing excepthook as a standalone module at some point.

Bumped version to 1.0.4.
Added __version__ attribute and README.md

Enabled scrolling of parent layout of locked digital outputs when mouse is over locked button
bumped patch version to v1.0.1

Ported excepthook to use tkinter rather than gtk.
This way it works regardless of what gui toolkits are installed.
Bumped major version number

Added camera_server.py, which provides a class CameraServer, for implementing
BIAS-like camera servers in Python.

Subclassing it and overriding a few methods is sufficient to have some Python
code interact with a BLACS Camera tab. A basic example is included of a real
camera server I used to simply save images to file which were acquired with
an external program that didn't require any configuration info from labscript.

A Python camera server implementing this protocol via subclassing CameraServer
can be as simple or complex as required, perhaps just saving images to file as
in the minimalistic example provided, or being in sole control of cameras and
programming them with labscript-set parameters, performing fits, displaying
images, allowing you to set ROIs etc. This class just provides the interface to
BLACS - what else your camera server does with hdf5 shot files and cameras is up
to you.
Bumped minor version number
Bumped patch version number for release.

Added check_version function to labscript_utils where it can be shared by
programs using it. Imports of this function will hard code the minimum version
they require for importing this function! (2.1.0)

Fixed bug in HorizontalHeaderViewWithWidgets, would display wrong geometry if
the widget was set before the item was set on a header section
Also a visual tweak.

Tweak to excepthook appearance. Testing complete for the moment.
